[[File:Spacegrazer.jpg|thumb|Illusory space grazers conjured up by Aleema Keto.]]
{{Quote|Out of the dark well of night they came, creatures born to the coldness of space. Devouring planets, swallowing stars, and drawing all ships to their deaths!|An illusion spell|audio=AleemaIllusion-DLotS.flac|<ref name="Tales of the Jedi: Dark Lords of the Sith (audio)">[[Tales of the Jedi: Dark Lords of the Sith (audio drama)|''Tales of the Jedi: Dark Lords of the Sith'' audio drama]]</ref>}}
'''Space grazers''' were legendary massive [[Realspace/Legends|space]]-dwelling lifeforms that were said to prey upon [[Starship/Legends|spaceships]]. They were believed to have gone extinct thousands of [[Standard year/Legends|years]] prior to [[4000 BBY/Legends|4000 BBY]].<ref name="darklords2">[[Tales of the Jedi – Dark Lords of the Sith 2|''Tales of the Jedi – Dark Lords of the Sith'' 2]]</ref>

During the [[Battle of Koros Major]], [[Aleema Keto]] created a [[Sith sorcery/Legends|magical]] [[Mind trick/Legends#Force illusion|illusion]] of space grazers in order to demoralize the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Republic Navy/Legends|fleet]] over [[Empress Teta/Legends|Koros Major]].<ref name="darklords2" />

